Following Standard Bank recently joining Samsung Pay’s early-access programme in South Africa, the company has launched new promotions. Standard Bank cards supported during early access are Mastercard credit and cheque cards. The following Samsung devices currently support Samsung Pay locally: Galaxy Note 8, S9, S8, S7, A8, and A5/A7 (2017 Edition). The Samsung Galaxy Note 9 will also be supported when it launches. The new promotional campaigns for Samsung Pay in South Africa are: More merchants and banks will be added to Samsung Pay in South Africa in the coming months, said Samsung.